### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَقَالُوا۟ قُلُوبُنَا غُلْفٌۢ ۚ بَل لَّعَنَهُمُ ٱللَّهُ بِكُفْرِهِمْ فَقَلِيلًا مَّا يُؤْمِنُونَ</span>

### English

They say, “Our hearts are unreceptive!” In fact, Allah has condemned them for their disbelief. They have but little faith.